            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/07/05/%e7%84%a1%e4%ba%ba%e6%a9%9f%e8%a1%a8%e6%bc%94-7-7-%e8%b3%80-anson-lo-%e7%94%9f%e6%97%a5-%e6%ad%b7%e6%99%82-12-%e5%88%86%e9%90%98-%e6%8f%90%e4%be%9b%e5%85%8d%e8%b2%bb%e6%b8%a1%e8%bc%aa/hottopic/walk/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Pickle Rick]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Fri, 05 Jul 2024 14:30:10 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[玩乐好去处]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Anson Lo]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[mirror]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[卢瀚霆]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1247993</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<div><p><span lang="ZH-TW">艺人卢瀚霆（</span>Anson Lo<span lang="ZH-TW">）将于 </span>7 <span lang="ZH-TW">月 </span>7 <span lang="ZH-TW">日迎来 </span>29 <span lang="ZH-TW">岁生日，其国际后援会为他筹备了一系列活动。</span><span lang="ZH-TW">其中包括 </span>7 <span lang="ZH-TW">月 </span>7 <span lang="ZH-TW">日晚上八时半在尖沙咀西九文化区上空举行的《</span>Anson Lo &amp; Sontos – SoaR <span lang="ZH-TW">无人机汇演》。汇演将展示多个与 </span>Anson Lo <span lang="ZH-TW">生日主题「</span>SoaR<span lang="ZH-TW">」相关的图案。</span></p></div><p><img decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1247994 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/449845310_1823439220-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/449845310_1823439220-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/449845310_1823439220.jpg 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/449845310_1823439220-144x144.jpg 144w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲7 <span lang="ZH-TW">月 </span>7 <span lang="ZH-TW">日晚上八时半在尖沙咀西九文化区上空举行《</span>Anson Lo &amp; Sontos – SoaR <span lang="ZH-TW">无人机汇演》（图片来源：<a href="https://www.facebook.com/share/p/emzuEVkgFxQ4i7uG/"><span class="xt0psk2"><span class="html-span xdj266r x11i5rnm xat24cr x1mh8g0r xexx8yu x4uap5 x18d9i69 xkhd6sd x1hl2dhg x16tdsg8 x1vvkbs">AnsonLohonting International Fan Club 卢瀚霆国际后援会 Facebook</span></span></a>）</span></p><div></div><div><p><span lang="ZH-TW">无人机汇演将历时 </span>12 <span lang="ZH-TW">分钟，成为香港首个以艺人为主题的无人机汇演。最佳观赏位置包括西九文化区艺术公园一带，以及香港故宫文化博物馆至艺术公园对开的海滨位置。后援会建议乐迷和市民分散到不同位置观赏，以免单一区域挤迫。</span></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1247995 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/450055903_1823439220-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/450055903_1823439220-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/450055903_1823439220.jpg 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/450055903_1823439220-144x144.jpg 144w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲<span lang="ZH-TW">最佳观赏位置包括西九文化区艺术公园一带（图片来源：<a href="https://www.facebook.com/share/p/emzuEVkgFxQ4i7uG/"><span class="xt0psk2"><span class="html-span xdj266r x11i5rnm xat24cr x1mh8g0r xexx8yu x4uap5 x18d9i69 xkhd6sd x1hl2dhg x16tdsg8 x1vvkbs">AnsonLohonting International Fan Club 卢瀚霆国际后援会 Facebook</span></span></a>）</span></p></div><div></div><div><p><span lang="ZH-TW">除了无人机汇演外，后援会亦安排了一系列庆祝活动，包括在尖沙咀天星码头对开的巨型 </span>LED <span lang="ZH-TW">大电视播放生日及舞台演出片段，并连续第三年提供免费渡轮服务。市民可以免费乘坐往来尖沙咀至湾仔的天星小轮。九龙塘又一城</span><span lang="ZH-TW">亦</span><span lang="ZH-TW">设</span><span lang="ZH-TW">有</span><span lang="ZH-TW">《</span>Anson Lo &amp; Sontos &#8211; SoaR Pop Up Store<span lang="ZH-TW">》，展出 </span>Anson Lo <span lang="ZH-TW">于 </span>MIRROR <span lang="ZH-TW">演唱会穿著过的水晶钻石战衣及多款限定周边商品，活动收入在扣除成本后将全数捐出作慈善用途。</span></p></div><p>资料及图片来源：<a href="https://www.facebook.com/share/p/emzuEVkgFxQ4i7uG/"><span class="xt0psk2"><span class="html-span xdj266r x11i5rnm xat24cr x1mh8g0r xexx8yu x4uap5 x18d9i69 xkhd6sd x1hl2dhg x16tdsg8 x1vvkbs">AnsonLohonting International Fan Club 卢瀚霆国际后援会 Facebook</span></span></a></p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/07/05/%e7%84%a1%e4%ba%ba%e6%a9%9f%e8%a1%a8%e6%bc%94-7-7-%e8%b3%80-anson-lo-%e7%94%9f%e6%97%a5-%e6%ad%b7%e6%99%82-12-%e5%88%86%e9%90%98-%e6%8f%90%e4%be%9b%e5%85%8d%e8%b2%bb%e6%b8%a1%e8%bc%aa/hottopic/walk/">无人机表演 7.7 贺 Anson Lo 生日，历时 12 分钟 + 提供免费渡轮</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
